description: Experience the essence of waterfront living in Residence 12G, a 2-Bed+Den, 2.5-Bath home offering stunning Southeastern views and abundant natural light. Wake up to the sunrise over the Atlantic and enjoy your morning coffee on your private terrace. With 1,942 sq. ft. of elegant living space, the open kitchen and living area, equipped with Wolf/Sub-Zero appliances, marble countertops, and custom Italian cabinetry, is perfect for hosting friends and family. Retreat to the serene primary suite with breathtaking views of the Boston Harbor Islands, dual closets, and a spa-inspired bath with heated floors. The versatile den makes an ideal home office, nursery, or flex space. Two garage parking spaces included and access to numerous private amenities, including guest suites, a 24-hour concierge, valet, doorman, complete the luxury lifestyle. As a resident, enjoy VIP status at St. Regis properties worldwide. Schedule your private tour today.
